<HEADLINE> S. Leone Accuses Liberian Pres.  </HEADLINE>
By CLARENCE ROY-MACAULAY
<TEXT>
<P>
   FREETOWN, Sierra Leone (AP) -- A senior military official accused
Liberia's president Saturday of hiring mercenaries to bolster
Sierra Leone's feared rebel movement. Liberian officials denied the
